    <h2>Introduction: Why Productivity Matters in 2026</h2>
    <p>In today's fast-paced professional world, <strong>productivity isn't just a buzzwordâ€”it's a survival skill</strong>. Whether you're a CEO managing teams, a freelancer juggling clients, or a student balancing academics, mastering productivity can transform your life.</p>
    <p>Studies show that highly productive professionals accomplish <strong>3x more than their peers</strong> while working fewer hours. The secret? They work smarter, not harder.</p>

    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4 my-6 rounded">
        <p class="font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-2">
