    <h2>3. Weekly Goal Setting</h2>
    <p>Set <strong>SMART goals</strong> every week: Specific, Measurable, Achievable, Relevant, Time-bound.</p>

    <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg my-4">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-2"><i class="fas fa-bullseye text-green-600 mr-2"></i>Goal Setting Framework:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Monday:</strong> Review last week & set 3-5 key goals</li>
            <li><strong>Daily:</strong> Break down goals into daily actions</li>
            <li><strong>Friday:</strong> Review progress and adjust</li>
            <li><strong>Sunday:</strong> Plan next week</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

